OL,4,Clinked to loyalist paramilitaries
OL,6,FThere was widespread criticism of the
OL,7,Fministers decision and today he faced
OL,8,Fquestions during an appearance before
OL,9,Fhis scrutiny committee on Thursday.
OL,11,FHe said he did not directly ask
OL,12,Frepresentatives of loyalist
OL,13,Fparamilitary gangs to end criminality
OL,14,Fduring a meeting with the umbrella
OL,15,Fgroup.
