OL,3,CGordon Lyons defends meeting group
OL,4,Clinked to loyalist paramilitaries
OL,6,FMr Lyons said there had been a
OL,7,F"misrepresentation" of his position
OL,8,Fsince the meeting.
OL,10,FHe said: "Unlike some, I will never
OL,11,Fseek to justify criminality or
OL,12,Fterrorism. Unlike some I will never
OL,13,Fglorify it and unlike some I will
OL,14,Fnever adhere to the notion that there
OL,15,Fis no alternative to violence."
OL,17,FMr Lyons told the committee the LCC
OL,18,Fwas representing those who "want to
OL,19,Fmove away from paramilitary activity".
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@SO]rD@JOUwD@_O]zD@\OU{D@eO]
