OL,3,CGordon Lyons defends meeting group
OL,4,Clinked to loyalist paramilitaries
OL,6,FThe minister added: "That is why I met
OL,7,Fwith them, to show what can be
OL,8,Fachieved through politics, to show
OL,9,Fthem the work I am doing in the
OL,10,Fdepartment to deal with some of the
OL,11,Fpressing issues facing communities
OL,12,Ftoday."
OL,14,FHe said it was "not accurate" to say a
OL,15,Fplatform had been given to the LCC
OL,16,Fwhich had not been given to other
OL,17,Fgroups, adding that the meeting had
OL,18,Ffocused on issues of deprivation and
OL,19,Fhousing.
