OL,4,Clinked to loyalist paramilitaries
OL,6,FMr Lyons added: "I made clear at the
OL,7,Fstart of the meeting of the importance
OL,8,Fof the democratic process."
OL,10,FHe told the committee that since he
OL,11,Fhad become minister he had received
OL,12,F763 invitations to attend meetings and
OL,13,Fhad attended or accepted 395.
OL,15,FSDLP MLA Daniel McCrossan said: "It is
OL,16,F26 years since the Good Friday
OL,17,FAgreement, surely there is no place in
OL,18,Four society for the LCC in today's
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland?"
OL,26,@nD@QOUpD@[O]wD@aOU{D@RO]
