OL,3,CGordon Lyons defends meeting group
OL,4,Clinked to loyalist paramilitaries
OL,6,FMr Lyons responded: "There is no place
OL,7,Ffor paramilitaries or paramilitary
OL,8,Factivity in our society today, but I
OL,9,Fthink there is a role for those
OL,10,Forganisations which say they are
OL,11,Fcommitted to moving forward and that
OL,12,Fthey are representing those who want
OL,13,Fto move forward."
OL,15,FAlliance Party MLA Sian Mulholland
OL,16,Fasked how the meeting complied with
OL,17,Fthe department's responsibility to
OL,18,Ftackle paramilitarism.
OL,26,@nD@UOUuD@QO]
