OL,3,CGordon Lyons defends meeting group
OL,4,Clinked to loyalist paramilitaries
OL,6,FMr Lyons said: "I have no truck
OL,7,Fwhatsoever with paramilitary activity,
OL,8,FI will oppose it at every opportunity.
OL,9,FThere is absolutely no contradiction
OL,10,Fthere whatsoever."
OL,12,FMs Mulholland said a number of groups
OL,13,Fshe had spoken to had expressed hurt
OL,14,Fand felt Mr Lyons' had "endorsed" the
OL,15,FLCC through the meeting.
OL,17,FUlster Unionist MLA Andy Allen asked
OL,18,Fthe minister if he accepted that the
OL,19,FLCC represented organisations which
OL,20,F"wreak havoc on our communities right
OL,21,Facross Northern Ireland?"
