OL,6,FMr Lyons said: "Yes, that is wrong and
OL,7,Fit shouldn't happen."
OL,9,FMr Gildernew said: "Did you actually
OL,10,Fask in the meeting for them to end
OL,11,Ftheir criminality?"
OL,13,FThe minister said: "Did I use those
OL,14,Fwords directly? No, I did not.
OL,16,F"I am happy to do that now but I think
OL,17,FI am being very clear when I say the
OL,18,Fonly way forward is through peaceful
OL,19,Fand democratic means.
